            <StreamGeometry x:Key="IconRefresh">M17.65 6.35A7.96 7.96 0 0 0 12 4a8 8 0 0 0-8 8a8 8 0 0 0 8 8c3.73 0 6.84-2.55 7.73-6h-2.08A5.99 5.99 0 0 1 12 18a6 6 0 0 1-6-6a6 6 0 0 1 6-6c1.66 0 3.14.69 4.22 1.78L13 11h7V4z</StreamGeometry>
            <StreamGeometry x:Key="IconCertificate">M9 10a3.04 3.04 0 0 1 3-3a3.04 3.04 0 0 1 3 3a3.04 3.04 0 0 1-3 3a3.04 3.04 0 0 1-3-3m3 9l4 1v-3.08A7.54 7.54 0 0 1 12 18a7.54 7.54 0 0 1-4-1.08V20m4-16a5.78 5.78 0 0 0-4.24 1.74A5.78 5.78 0 0 0 6 10a5.78 5.78 0 0 0 1.76 4.23A5.78 5.78 0 0 0 12 16a5.78 5.78 0 0 0 4.24-1.77A5.78 5.78 0 0 0 18 10a5.78 5.78 0 0 0-1.76-4.26A5.78 5.78 0 0 0 12 4m8 6a8 8 0 0 1-.57 2.8A7.8 7.8 0 0 1 18 15.28V23l-6-2l-6 2v-7.72A7.9 7.9 0 0 1 4 10a7.68 7.68 0 0 1 2.33-5.64A7.73 7.73 0 0 1 12 2a7.73 7.73 0 0 1 5.67 2.36A7.68 7.68 0 0 1 20 10</StreamGeometry>
            <StreamGeometry x:Key="IconPlus">M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6z</StreamGeometry>
            <StreamGeometry x:Key="IconAppWindow">M15 9H5V5h10m-3 14a3 3 0 0 1-3-3a3 3 0 0 1 3-3a3 3 0 0 1 3 3a3 3 0 0 1-3 3m5-16H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7z</StreamGeometry>
